# Week 1 — Task 1: Zero-Shot vs Few-Shot Showdown

**Aila Nasir · Generative AI & Prompt Engineering Intern · NeuroFive Solutions**

## Prompt Used (Zero-Shot)
Classify the following customer support messages as one of: Complaint, Question, or Praise. Return only the label for each message.

1. "My order arrived three days late and no one responded to my emails."
2. "Does this product come in a larger size?"
3. "Absolutely loved the quality, will order again!"
4. "The app keeps crashing every time I try to checkout."
5. "How long does delivery usually take?"
6. "Your support team was so helpful, thank you!"
7. "I was charged twice for the same order."
8. "Can I change my shipping address after placing the order?"
9. "The packaging was nice but the item arrived late."
10. "Is there a discount for bulk orders?"

## Zero-Shot Results

**ChatGPT:** Complaint, Question, Praise, Complaint, Question, Praise, Complaint, Question, Complaint, Question

**Claude:** Complaint, Question, Praise, Complaint, Question, Praise, Complaint, Question, Complaint, Question

